  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Global Alliance for Tax Justice</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Please see attached Outline Description in full.  GATJ is at a crucial phase of its development and needs funding to:  &#x2022; Establish the Global Alliance&apos;s International Secretariat as the central communications hub that facilitates global campaigning efforts and promotes a united global civil society voice on tax justice issues. &#x2022; Launch the first global umbrella campaign to make multinational corporations pay their fair share of tax and invest the funds in public services for all to end inequality and poverty.   Without support from larger organisations like Oxfam, GATJ risks not being able to get together as a global campaigning organisation.  They are a crucial partner for our Inequality campaign, given their wide base of support from organisations working on tax in the South.  By supporting them in this critical start up phase, we will be able to work closely with the membership to align their campaigning activities and our Inequality campaign asks as much as possible.</narrative>
  </description>
